Per Mertesacker on Arsenal partnering with Werder Bremen: &ldquo;Werder Bremen has a very good youth system &amp; with Thomas [Schaaf; Bremen technical director], who brings in new structures. I talked to him &amp; thought about what we can do together as far as players are concerned.&rdquo; [BILD]<br />
<br />
Mertesacker on #afc youngsters loaned to the Bundesliga: &ldquo;In Germany, you are challenged in the regional league. The step from our U23s into the first-team is even bigger, because the next highest level is the PL. Therefore, for us, loans in the Bundesliga are very attractive.&rdquo;
